title: DJ's Top 25 Rookies & Week 5 Preview
itunes:title: DJ's Top 25 Rookies & Week 5 Preview
description:
Which first-year players are off to a hot start? Daniel Jeremiah reveals which rookies have impressed through four weeks of the season (1:20). DJ and Bucky then preview every week 5 game and turn up the pressure on franchises that desperately need a win this weekend (16:25). As always, the Move the Sticks team caps the Thursday show by picking the biggest week 6 college football games including the Red River Rivalry (40:53).
